{"id": "2192", "post": "<div class=\"post-2192 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-easyvds-net tag-uk tag-vmware\" id=\"post-2192\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/easyvds-4-40-512mb-vmware-vps-in-uk/\" rel=\"bookmark\">EasyVDS \u2013 \u00a34.40 512MB VMWare VPS in UK</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/easyvds-net/\" rel=\"tag\">easyvds.net</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/uk/\" rel=\"tag\">uk</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/vmware/\" rel=\"tag\">vmware</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> October 19, 2011 @ 3:35 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://easyvds.net/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/images/easyvds.jpg\" data-src=\"/media/images/easyvds.jpg\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" alt=\"EasyVDS\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a> <a href=\"http://easyvds.net/\"><b>EasyVDS</b></a>, part of <a href=\"http://ccpg.co.uk/\">CCPG Solutions</a>, are selling some cheap UK-based <a href=\"http://easyvds.net/linux-vps/\">VMWare Linux VPS</a>, starting from \u00a32.50/month. For 512M plan it\u2019s <b>\u00a34.40/month</b> (~USD$6.92), and you can <a href=\"https://portal.ccpgsolutions.net/order/?pid=39&amp;skip=1&amp;systpl=easyvds\">sign up here</a> (<em>note: pro-rata to the end of the month</em>).</p><ul><li>512MB memory</li><li>15GB storage</li><li>1TB/month data transfer</li><li>VMWare/Custom control panel</li></ul><p>Payment in PayPal, Moneybookers, credit card or bank transfer. They are using a custom control panel integrated with WHMCS to do simple VPS management (reboot, rDNS, etc). Their servers are with BlueSquare in Maidenhead, UK. CCGS Solutions LTD was registered in March 2009 in UK (Company No. 06852472). It seems to be run by Adam and Jacob who are currently studying in University of Portsmouth but also wear quite a few hats at the same time.</p><p>Cheap VMware based offers are a bit hard to come by. eNetSouth had some equivalent offers in Chicago and San Jose (although from what I\u2019ve seen, there seems to be quite a bit of support problem right now), and then <a href=\"/blog/vmstormvps-5-97-256mb-vmware-vps-in-state-college-pa/\">this VMStormVPS offer</a> with lower memory, but this is the first one in UK.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Feasyvds-4-40-512mb-vmware-vps-in-uk%2F&amp;t=EasyVDS%20-%20%C2%A34.40%20512MB%20VMWare%20VPS%20in%20UK\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=EasyVDS%20-%20%C2%A34.40%20512MB%20VMWare%20VPS%20in%20UK&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Feasyvds-4-40-512mb-vmware-vps-in-uk%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com